<br>
I play on a blue server, and to tell the truth, i would be happy about manaburn nerf. I feel somewhat useless besides manaburn wizards...<br>
<br>
Now, this is not the way to do it.<br>
<br>
Critical removed ok.<br>
Target cap introduced - I think its bad.<br>
<br>
SeravTrev idea about not leaving corpse if more than 50% (or 75% or 90%) of damage is done by manaburn is ok. Making a mob who suffered manaburn immune to manaburn for 30sec (or 10sec or 60sec) is ok. The skill still has its usefullness, its just that you have to rely on other tactics too, so other classes too, to get out a mob.<br>
<br>
In EQ groups are powerful if they have a good mix. Teamwork is important. That creates the fun of the game. But if 6 wizards can take out anything, we do not speak about skill anymore. I am glad if it gets nerfed, but I do not like it nerfed this way.<br>
